<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->

    <title>Welcome to DUMENA Education</title>
    <style>
        .btn:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <table
        style="border-collapse: collapse; border: #ccc solid thin; width: 400px; margin: auto; font: normal 14px 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif"
        cellpadding="17">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 15px;">
                <img src="https://demo.dumena.com/assets/img/logo.svg" style="padding: 30px; width: 160px;"
                    alt="Dumena Logo" />
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p>Dear {{ user }},</p>

                <p>We got a request to reset your DUMENA password. If you didn't initiate this request, please
                    ignore this email; if you did please click on the button below to reset you password.</p>
                <br>
                <a href="{{url}}" style="text-decoration: none;
                    color: #fff;
                    background-color: #DF7829;
                    border-radius: 5px;
                    box-shadow: inset 0 3px 5px rgba(0,0,0,.125);
                    margin-bottom: 0;
                    font-weight: 400;
                    text-align: center;
                    white-space: nowrap;
                    vertical-align: middle;
                    -ms-touch-action: manipulation;
                    touch-action: manipulation;
                    cursor: pointer;
                    -webkit-user-select: none;
                    -moz-user-select: none;
                    -ms-user-select: none;
                    user-select: none;
                    background-image: none;
                    height: 46px;
                    padding: 10px 16px;
                    font-size: 18px;
                    line-height: 1.3333333;
                ">Reset Password</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><br>
                <p>
                    Regards,<br>
                    DUMENA Team.<br>
                    support@dumena.com
                </p>
                <br>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px 10px; background: #e0e0e0; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;">
                Information in this message is confidential. If you are not the intended recipient, please notify the
                sender and delete the
                message from your system immediately. Please note that we apply spam filters. If you do not receive a
                reply to an
                important message, please contact DUMENA EDUCATION by telephone or email.
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

</body>

</html>